OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Ffurther rain, and turning to snow to
OL,7,Fquite low levels over inland Moray,
OL,8,Fand Upper Deeside. Easterly winds
OL,9,Fbecoming northwest, severe gale for
OL,10,Ftime. Drier by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSome bright, sunny spells
OL,13,Ffirst thing. Then cloudier for a time
OL,14,Fwith some showers, wintry on high
OL,15,Fground. Bright spells and showers in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Blustery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
